public class ProcessorUnknown
extends ProcessorTemplateElem

**For internal use only** This class processes an unknown template element, and ignores the startElement and endElement events. It is used both for unknown top-level elements, and for elements in the xslt namespace when the version is higher than the version of XSLT that we are set up to process.
